| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5031 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 83821e9d-054c-5591-9bdb-0bbef6478f39"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
